.TH smi-gintra-mount-location "1" "October 2025" "SMI Toolset 0.100.0" "SMI Gintra Command"
.SH NAME
smi-gintra-mount-location \- Print the SMI Gintra mount directory location
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B smi-gintra-mount-location
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
.B smi-gintra-mount-location
prints the path to the directory where the Gintra filesystem is expected to be mounted, typically \fB/mnt/gintra\fR.
.SH AUTHOR
.PP
Command written by Imre Tabur.
Documentation written by Imre Tabur.
.SH "REPORTING BUGS"
.PP
Report smi-gintra-mount-location bugs to \fIinfo@setmy.info\fR
.SH "SEE ALSO"
.PP
.BR smi-gintra-location (1)

